---
import Base from "../../layouts/Base.astro";
---
<Base
  title="Guides — ai-tracker"
  description="Practical guides for builders: per-provider quickstarts, deploy recipes, model-selection walkthroughs."
>
  <h1>Guides</h1>
  <p>Practical reference for working AI builders. Each guide is opinionated — picks a default, lists alternatives, surfaces the gotchas.</p>

  <ul class="guide-list">
    <li class="guide-card">
      <a href="/guides/quickstart" class="card-link">
        <h2>Quickstart per provider</h2>
        <p>60-second per-provider quickstarts: get a key, make your first request in curl, Python, Node. Covers Anthropic, OpenAI, Google, Mistral, Meta (via OpenRouter).</p>
      </a>
    </li>
  </ul>

  <p class="muted small">
    More guides planned: deploy recipes (LangGraph + Claude on Vercel, Anything-LLM on Fly), model-selection decision trees (companion to <a href="/picker">/picker</a>), provider-migration walkthroughs.
  </p>

  <style>
    .guide-list { list-style: none; padding: 0; margin: 1.5rem 0; display: grid; gap: 0.8rem; }
    .guide-card { background: var(--surface); border: 1px solid var(--line); border-radius: 8px; }
    .card-link { display: block; padding: 1.1rem 1.2rem; color: inherit; text-decoration: none; }
    .card-link:hover { background: var(--surface-soft); border-radius: 8px; }
    .guide-card h2 { margin: 0 0 0.4rem; font-size: 1.15rem; }
    .guide-card p { margin: 0; font-size: 0.95rem; line-height: 1.5; color: #4f5a6d; }
    .muted { color: var(--muted); }
    .small { font-size: 0.88rem; }
  </style>
</Base>
